The paper deals with optimization of resource allocation in wireless communication systems, specifically in MIMO multicell networks. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also involves coordination of multiple cells, which falls under the category of control and systems engineering (cs.SY). The use of precoding techniques and optimization algorithms falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia systems (cs.MM).
